               <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_005-53a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-01-31T17:19:06.049+09:00">make a decision in accordance with/based on laws and regulations</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_013-2a.49" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-01-31T17:26:05.698+09:00">then the laws and regulations/administrative procedures and rules of the former kings were sometimes adjusted.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_013-4a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-01-31T17:52:41.297+09:00">The laws and regulations and the legal decisions are in each case adapted to what is appropriate.</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_013-9a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-01-31T17:53:35.797+09:00">the laws and regulations</seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-21a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-01-31T18:00:56.826+09:00">It wasn't that there were no laws and regulations/administrative procedures</seg>
            <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_001-5a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T00:33:09.069+09:00">Thus the affairs of this sublunar world</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_001-5a.54" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T00:36:32.762+09:00">Everyone in the world rallies to him</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_001-6a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T00:38:33.173+09:00">He expands the boundaries of what there is in this sublunar world.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_001-17a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T00:42:05.835+09:00">The things in this sublunar world</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_001-26a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T00:57:32.599+09:00">Thought little of the political world</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_001-26a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T01:02:23.204+09:00">The most important thing in the world</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_012-57a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T22:28:29.206+09:00">1.　是：以為是。天下人认为这是臣子弑君而下讨伐上，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_012-57a.44" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T22:32:25.276+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_013-3a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T22:36:44.832+09:00">The geographical versus the sociopolitical readengs</seg>
